{"tid":1648610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛重要｝舉辦活動指引上線啦","createTime":"2019-10-12T09:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T23:43:00.000Z","uid":14921,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d109717f5a2c64d7af8d2bb11447b16d78b5e2","tid":1648610,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">前言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於目前活動繁多，致活動人數未能集中及宣傳時間不足，故此訂立舉辦活動指引，以供搞手們作參考。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一。宣傳期</span></span><br />\n活動舉辦必須預留一星期作宣傳期，請善用文宣谷及連登洗地谷（推上熱門），儘快加入日程表，以加大宣傳力度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二。活動日期安排</span></span><br />\n<br />\n活動日期分為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平日活動</span></span> 及 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">週末活動</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n週末活動以遊行/集會為首要，若多於一個活動舉辦，則以遊行為先，其他活動應積極考慮改期。<br />\n<br />\n其他活動例如和你唱，和你拖，摺紙鷂則應安排於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平日</span></span>，以不影響遊行舉辦為大原則。"},{"pid":"239fa883e3b14a76865534482f3c8b86b220264c","tid":1648610,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家仲有咩建議"},{"pid":"2440b65c1fd4568d7a991d38e2a0996334ca2dd8","tid":1648610,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e82fc29ec7e07e89819692bea2a21be92587915","tid":1648610,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"10月6日至10月7日 以下句子一直蔓延 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&quot;<strong>等美國通過法案啦 忍下手啦 唔差在呢幾日啦, 我地比律師朋友做野啦 休息啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br 